Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.98,Sign_Basic,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\b1\an3\fs30\bord0\shad0\pos(608,305)}20:38 Shibuya Hikarie B3F
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.53,0:00:18.37,Italics,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:25.12,Italics,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,There's another veil centered underneath \Nhere that also traps non-sorcerers inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.84,0:00:31.46,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:34.97,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,Hup, hup.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.56,0:00:45.10,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,I think I have a good idea what they're after.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:50.11,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll play along.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.11,0:00:53.86,Sign_Basic,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\b1\an1\fs30\bord0\shad0\pos(32,305)}20:39 Aoyama Cemetery
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.90,0:00:53.86,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}They're making Gojo-sensei do this alone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.28,0:00:58.41,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,I understand the logic, but there \Nhas to be something we can do, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.41,0:01:00.03,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Be his backup or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:01.45,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.91,0:01:08.38,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That's why we're heading to Shibuya now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:10.09,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.09,0:01:11.21,Main,UiUi,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.21,0:01:12.32,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,"Give it back"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.38,0:01:17.34,Main,UiUi,0000,0000,0000,,Forcing Nee-sama to be his backup...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:21.18,Main,UiUi,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru Gojo must think he's some big-shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.18,0:01:24.93,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't treat him \Nlike some ordinary guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:28.73,Main,Ui,0000,0000,0000,,You're not like ordinary \Nwomen yourself, Nee-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:30.44,Sign_Basic,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS\an8\c&H121617&\3c&H727678&\bord1\shad0\move(316,58,290,58)}Some Ordinary Guy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:30.44,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Ui Ui!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.44,0:01:33.19,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,You truly are adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.19,0:01:35.53,Main,Ui,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}There you go saying stuff \Nyou don't believe again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.61,0:01:41.08,Sign_Basic,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\fnArial\b1\an1\fs20\bord0\shad0\fscx85\q2\pos(32,250)}Team Mei Mei\h\hMei Mei (Grade 1 Jujutsu Sorcerer)\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hUi Ui\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hYuji Itadori (Promotion Evaluation Postponed)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:41.08,Main,Ui,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What you love isn't family, but work \Nrelations treated as family relations, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:44.12,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,You really do get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.12,0:01:46.16,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I love that part of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:46.91,Main,Ui,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:48.96,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry up and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.54,0:01:52.17,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Mei Mei here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.63,0:01:53.46,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.59,0:01:58.38,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Itadori-kun, change in destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:01:59.18,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:02:03.68,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Another veil like the one over Shibuya \Nwas lowered over Meiji Shrine Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.68,0:02:05.79,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading to that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:11.11,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,We're running. Keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:12.77,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:20.11,Sign_Basic,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,525)\fnArial\b1\an1\fs30\bord0\shad0\pos(182,250)}20:40\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h{\fs22}Tokyo Metro, Shibuya Station\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hB5F, Shin-toshin Line Platform
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:25.49,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,I see you're all fully prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.77,0:02:31.44,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,You came.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:34.68,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,You won't have any excuses left \Nwhen you lose this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:40.01,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,And have you given thought to the \Nfirst excuse you'll use when you lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.01,0:02:43.01,Ep_Title,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 32\N{\fs30\fscy150}Shibuya Incident
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:58.07,Show_Title,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,825)\pos(320,10)}JUJUTSU KAISEN\N{\fs16\bord0\fscy100\c&HDEDCE0&}Shibuya Incident
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:18.98,Sign_Basic,Map,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H525D5B&\frz332.5\bord0\shad0\b1\move(176,92,176,286)}Platform
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.14,0:04:16.45,Main,Assistant Supervisor,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}There's a veil to keep \Nordinary people trapped inside
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.45,0:04:18.98,Main,Assistant Supervisor,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}covering the entire \Nunderground subway station,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:22.65,Main,Assistant Supervisor,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}and within that, there's another \Nveil centered around the platform
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:25.66,Sign_Basic,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\b1\an1\fs30\bord0\shad0\pos(136,265)}20:51 \h\h\h\h\h\h\h{\fs24}\hTokyo Metro, Meiji Shrine Station\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hExit 2
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:25.66,Main,Assistant Supervisor,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}on level B5 that prevents \Nsorcerers from entering.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:30.29,Main,Assistant Supervisor,0000,0000,0000,,We believe the cursed spirit or \Ncurse user who lowered these veils
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:32.35,Main,Assistant Supervisor,0000,0000,0000,,is located somewhere between these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:34.00,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Between them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.58,0:04:37.00,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Not on the platform they're centered around?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:41.63,Main,Assistant Supervisor,0000,0000,0000,,We believe they're most likely taking \Non the risk of being outside
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:44.38,Main,Assistant Supervisor,0000,0000,0000,,the veil as well in order \Nto strengthen the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:47.36,Main,Assistant Supervisor,0000,0000,0000,,Two of our assistant supervisors \Nhave already been taken out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:50.43,Main,Assistant Supervisor,0000,0000,0000,,Also, in between these barriers...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:56.10,Main,Assistant Supervisor,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we can't say for certain yet, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:04:59.36,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine. Say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:08.62,Main,Assistant Supervisor,0000,0000,0000,,There are transfigured \Nhumans between the barriers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:33.81,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two doing?! We have to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:34.48,Main,Ui,0000,0000,0000,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:38.27,Main,Ui,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-sama is currently sharing \Nthe crows' perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:41.57,Main,Ui,0000,0000,0000,,It's a process that takes \Nconcentration, so be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:44.61,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind if you talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:45.44,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,She says it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:48.03,Main,Ui,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:53.41,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:56.33,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I've got the gist of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:05:58.21,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Itadori-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:06:01.21,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,which would you prefer? \NKilling lots of weak, transfigured humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:04.13,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,or exorcising one powerful cursed spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:09.59,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing you, it's probably the latter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:15.89,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,This is a map of the underground station.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:18.39,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,The transfigured humans are mulling about
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:21.02,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,and attacking normal people here, on level B4.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:27.19,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,The majority of the normal people are \Nprobably at the train platform on level B5.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:29.66,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,"Probably"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:32.91,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,The crows I used are imbued \Nwith cursed energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:35.91,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,so they couldn't enter B5.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:41.38,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm guessing they're forcing normal people \Nto flee to B5, and serving them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:47.38,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Also, my crows got hunted \Ndown here, between B1 and B2.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:51.43,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,This is likely where the cursed spirit \Nor curse user who lowered the veil is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:55.60,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they're planning to hunt down \Nany common people that come back up,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:57.98,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,or maybe it has something to do \Nwith the veils' conditions,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.98,0:06:59.85,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,but it's unclear why they've chosen
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:03.71,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,this positioning, and what they hope \Nto achieve by isolating level B5.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:07.65,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,He's here, though, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.58,0:07:09.90,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Right below us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:11.82,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,That curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:14.07,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:19.08,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,My crows all got killed before they \Ncould confirm seeing Patchface.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:23.58,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Though the presence of transfigured \Nhumans would suggest that's likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:26.92,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not so sure about dividing up our forces,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:30.88,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,but if we keep wasting time, all the \Ncommon people on B4 will be wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:37.76,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us will take Exit 7 directly \Nto B4 and rescue the civilians.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.31,0:07:42.14,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,If it gets too dangerous, \Nyou head down there, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:46.86,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Though, if I can be greedy, \NI hope that by the time we reunite,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:50.24,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,the veil will be lifted, \Nthe civilians will be freed,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:54.87,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,and we'll know what our \Nopponent on B5 is after.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:07:58.04,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Mei-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:08:02.16,Sign_Basic,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\b1\an8\fs26\bord0\shad0\pos(320,225)}21:03 Tokyo Metro, Meiji Shrine Station, B2F
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:01.46,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:16.76,Main,Ko-guy,0000,0000,0000,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:31.19,Main,Ko-guy,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're a j-juchu... j-jujuchu... \Njuju... jujutsu sorcerer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:34.45,Main,Ko-guy,0000,0000,0000,,A jujutsu sorcerer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:35.61,Main,Ko-guy,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:37.82,Main,Ko-guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:41.25,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,The patchfaced cursed spirit is here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:42.37,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:47.58,Main,Ko-guy,0000,0000,0000,,Patch... face? Patchface?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:50.75,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,The one with stitches all over his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:54.09,Main,Ko-guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't insult me! I know that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.09,0:08:56.34,Main,Ko-guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm clever!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:58.55,Main,Ko-guy,0000,0000,0000,,Mahito is below.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:01.85,Main,Ko-guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here protecting the veil.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:03.48,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Mahito...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:06.35,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,I think Junpei called him that, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:09.38,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,No, its name doesn't matter right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.74,0:09:12.21,Flashback,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,Barriers are pretty complicated, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:15.49,Flashback,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,There are plenty of people who \Nare strong and still can't do them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:17.64,Flashback,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,Though I'm both strong and capable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:21.33,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,This thing is responsible for \Nthe veil? Both of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:22.58,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't seem likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:27.83,Main,Ko-guy,0000,0000,0000,,Mahito's sorcery is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:32.63,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,He did say he was "protecting the veil."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:34.97,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Which makes that object very suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:36.63,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll smash it for starters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:38.01,Main,Ko-guy,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:41.93,Main,Ko-guy,0000,0000,0000,,The humans he transfigures \Nlose their flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.43,0:09:48.10,Main,Ko-guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm clever, so I can tell the difference!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:10:04.41,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,All of you need to stop \Nunderestimating humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:13.21,Main,Ko-guy,0000,0000,0000,,I take it y-you're not clever, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:18.01,Main,Ko-guy,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know what curse I am, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:20.34,Main,Ko-guy,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:26.93,Main,Ko-guy,0000,0000,0000,,The not-clever ones die first in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:29.98,Sign_Basic,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs12\fnTimes New Roman\b1\c&H152C35&\3c&HB1C1CC&\bord1\shad0\move(475,80,481,73)}You look just like one
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:30.00,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're a grasshopper curse, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:31.06,Main,Ko-guy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:40.91,Italics,Ko-guy,0000,0000,0000,,This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:43.33,Italics,Ko-guy,0000,0000,0000,,is clever!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:49.04,Show_Title,Eyecatch,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1350,0)\1c&H75EFED&\3c&H75EFED&\blur20\1a&HE0&\3a&HC0&\pos(320,18)}JUJUTSU KAISEN
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:49.04,Show_Title,Eyecatch,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1350,0)\1a&HFF&\3c&HC5E3EC&\pos(320,18)}JUJUTSU KAISEN
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:54.04,Show_Title,Eyecatch,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(675,0)\3c&H1EDDF0&\pos(320,18)\c&H292619&}JUJUTSU KAISEN
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:55.42,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,Locust plague.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:59.59,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,A large-scale disaster arising \Nfrom an outbreak of locusts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:03.76,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,The locusts will consume not just crops,\Nbut paper, clothes, buildings—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:07.14,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,anything and everything \Nmade from plant fibers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:12.60,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,A locust is required to eat its own \Nweight in food every day to grow,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:15.23,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,so a locust swarm weighing one ton
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:19.61,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,must consume 2,500 people's \Nworth of food each day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:23.29,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,The abnormal sounds of chewing fill the \Nair around the swarm all day and night,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.29,0:11:25.83,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,and once the swarm has passed,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.83,0:11:30.12,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,it leaves behind a wasteland covered \Nin the black fluid secreted by locusts,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:33.54,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,creating a sight that is far from tranquil.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:40.63,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,Mankind has long feared, hated, \Nand cursed such demonic pests.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:48.85,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,What an incredible jaw and jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:52.64,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that it can understand speech \Nmeans it's decently powerful, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.44,0:12:41.28,Main,Ko-guy,0000,0000,0000,,You keep just running away...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:43.24,Main,Ko-guy,0000,0000,0000,,Which is it with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:46.41,Italics,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,He probably doesn't have any tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:47.74,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Which what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:49.62,Main,Ko-guy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you clever?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:52.00,Main,Ko-guy,0000,0000,0000,,Or not clever?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:55.75,Main,Ko-guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:13:01.27,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Clever people wouldn't really go \Naround calling themselves clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:03.30,Main,Ko-guy,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:30.49,Main,Ko-guy,0000,0000,0000,,Time to go fist-to-fist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:32.83,Main,Ko-guy,0000,0000,0000,,Your two arms
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:35.16,Main,Ko-guy,0000,0000,0000,,versus my four.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:58.90,Italics,Ko-guy,0000,0000,0000,,My arms, my jaw, and my eyes \Nare all superior to those of humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:01.40,Italics,Ko-guy,0000,0000,0000,,So why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:11.28,Italics,Ko-guy,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I the only one getting hit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.01,0:14:36.93,Main,Ko-guy,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I am the more clever one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:39.98,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,Locusts lay their eggs underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:43.52,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,To facilitate this, they're capable of extending \Ntheir abdomens, the tips of which are hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:47.28,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,to nearly three times their normal length.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.07,0:14:51.74,Main,Ko-guy,0000,0000,0000,,I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:14:59.71,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,He did have a trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:02.17,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,But more importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:04.46,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,You've eaten people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:07.30,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,You're prepared for what that means, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:14.01,Narration,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,There was a gap in their strength \Nthat no trick could overcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:19.60,Main,Ui,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:21.31,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.59,0:15:23.27,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,The veil is lifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.61,0:15:26.78,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wait for Itadori-kun \Nand then descend to B5.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:36.08,Sign_Basic,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\b1\an1\fs30\bord0\shad0\pos(142,250)}21:14\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h{\fs24}Tokyo Metro, Meiji Shrine Station\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hB5F Shin-toshin Line Platform
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.24,0:15:33.66,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ko-guy was exorcised, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:36.08,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That means a skilled sorcerer is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:41.83,Sign_Basic,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\b1\an8\c&H455051&\3c&HF1FFFF&\shad0}Meiji Shrine (Harajuku)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.99,0:15:38.33,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:40.83,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to fight them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:44.54,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:48.05,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Got a job to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:52.34,Main,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\b1\an1\fs30\bord0\shad0\pos(48,305)}21:15\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h{\fs24}Tokyo Metro, Meiji Shrine Station B4F
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:52.34,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Impressive, Itadori-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.13,0:15:54.09,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,What was?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:59.18,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I thought you \Nwould struggle a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:03.06,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,You're practically a first-grade already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:07.36,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen anyone get this far \Nwithout a technique since Kusakabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.02,0:16:09.99,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't Patchface.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:13.11,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd been fighting him, \Nit wouldn't have gone as easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:15.45,Main,Ui,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-sama is praising you! Just accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.45,0:16:16.99,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! I'm honored!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:24.75,Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Guess we're too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:26.44,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.44,0:16:27.67,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:30.17,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the other...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.35,0:16:43.20,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to do all this. I won't run.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:48.19,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, if I ran, you guys would \Nkill every human in here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:52.44,Sign_Basic,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fnTimes New Roman\b1\fs18\shad0\c&H000000&\3c&HCED5DB&}That's the whole reason\NI came here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:55.03,Main,YouthA,0000,0000,0000,,What are those two talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:56.45,Main,YouthB,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you mean "four"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:17:00.20,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,If you ran, huh? The correct answer is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:05.83,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand when Satoru Gojo is \Nable to utilize his power to the fullest?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:11.96,Flashback,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Quit with the build-up and say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:13.76,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.49,0:17:17.30,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,when he's alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:20.68,Flashback,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,The correct answer is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:23.14,Main,Youths,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:27.81,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you run or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.94,0:17:33.94,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,Get back or you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:37.78,Italics,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so they sealed the exit \Noff earlier to create a blind
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:41.08,Sign_Basic,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman\b1\c&H1D1D19&\3c&HB8BBB3&\shad0\frz359.7\pos(76,115.334)}Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:41.08,Sign_Basic,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman\b1\c&H1D1D19&\3c&HB8BBB3&\shad0\fs17\frz3.858\pos(88,284.667)}Can't Break It
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:41.08,Sign_Basic,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS\b1\c&H1D1D19&\3c&HB8BBB3&\shad0\fs17\frz3.858\fs12\pos(168,74.667)}Eek!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:41.58,Italics,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,so I wouldn't know if there were \Npeople on the other side or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:46.60,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,Any jujutsu sorcerer with him \Nis basically just a hindrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:51.71,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,So we'll go one step lower and completely \Nsurround him with non-sorcerers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.35,0:18:13.36,Main,Choso,0000,0000,0000,,Blood Manipulation: Slicing Exorcism.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:38.88,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,The minimum output of his cursed technique \Nreversal is double that of his amplification.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:42.80,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be nearly impossible for him to use it \Nwithout catching non-sorcerers in it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:47.90,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,He probably won't be able to charge his \NBlue up to an effective output, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:54.90,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,It should prove difficult for him to use \NBlue for high-speed movement, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:58.92,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,It would make him a dump truck as \Nfar as non-sorcerers are concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.92,0:19:00.78,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,Get hit and it's instant death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:05.91,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,So in that situation, Satoru Gojo will \Nhave to focus his energy on defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:11.92,Sign_Basic,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(209.333,198.667)\fnComic Sans MS\c&H975B87&\3c&HCCB2AD&\shad0\b1\fs16}Hmph
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:19.97,Main,Jogo&Hanami,0000,0000,0000,,Domain Amplification!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.07,0:19:46.62,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,Makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:50.29,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose you would think of \Nthat after allying with curse users.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.37,0:19:53.04,Italics,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,Domain Amplification...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:55.96,Italics,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same principle as the \NNew Shadow School's simple domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.39,0:19:58.84,Italics,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,They envelop themselves with the domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.84,0:20:00.72,Italics,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,While that reduces its \Nguaranteed-hit effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:03.64,Italics,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,it ensures they neutralize \Nany technique used.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.93,0:20:11.16,Italics,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,That would allow their attacks to hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.50,0:20:15.40,Flashback,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do about his \Ndomain, Infinite Void?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:22.15,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,The only ones unaffected by Infinite Void are \NSatoru Gojo himself and anyone he touches.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:29.92,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he does have the skill \Nto selectively trap you all in it,
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.91,0:20:35.17,Sign_Basic,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H3A403E&\3c&HE7EFE9&\shad0\pos(110.667,30.667)}Veil
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.92,0:20:32.23,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,a great number of non-sorcerers \Nwould get crushed
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.23,0:20:35.17,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,to death in the space left \Nbetween his domain and the veil.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.29,0:20:35.17,Sign_Basic,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(125,0)\pos(506.667,191.333)\fnTimes New Roman\b1\c&H000000&\3c&HFCF4F5&\bord1\shad0\blur1\frz301.8}Infinite Void
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.29,0:20:35.17,Sign_Basic,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(125,0)\fnTimes New Roman\b1\c&H221DDC&\3c&HFCF4F5&\bord1\shad0\blur1\pos(521.333,106.667)\frz310.3}Ack!
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.29,0:20:35.17,Sign_Basic,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(125,0)\fnTimes New Roman\b1\c&H221DDC&\3c&HFCF4F5&\bord1\shad0\blur1\frz46.97\pos(172,137.333)}Ack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:39.92,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,Chances are 99% that he won't use his domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:44.45,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,But that means you mustn't \Nuse your domains, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.45,0:20:47.22,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,If you draw a large mass of \Nnon-sorcerers into your domain,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.22,0:20:51.27,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,he'll be forced to give up \Non them and use his, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:54.93,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,And you already realize that you can't \Nwin a tug-of-war of domains, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.94,0:21:01.19,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, you just need \Nto get Satoru Gojo to focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:04.61,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,Focus on defeating cursed spirits \Nand rescuing non-sorcerers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.78,0:21:11.33,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.80,0:21:13.87,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, keep it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.62,0:21:15.79,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,You're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:18.33,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, take my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.59,0:21:26.30,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I told you not to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.43,0:21:29.97,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Can you not understand unless I do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:33.31,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.64,0:21:35.89,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I'm shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.89,0:21:38.90,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,What? Making excuses?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.52,0:21:41.23,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all, baldy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.49,0:21:52.54,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying I'm shocked that you ever thought \Nyou could beat me if this is all you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.54,0:21:59.33,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,I'll want you to hold out \Nfor at least twenty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.67,0:22:05.13,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,After that, it's time for me \Nand the Prison Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.27,0:23:42.82,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,Time for the Yamanote Line Game! \NThe topic is Satoru Gojo's good points!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.82,0:23:44.17,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.17,0:23:45.20,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.46,0:23:46.56,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.80,0:23:47.74,Main,Kugisaki,0000,0000,0000,,Only strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.74,0:23:49.56,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "Shibuya Incident - Gate, Open."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.78,0:24:27.86,Next_Ep_Title,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\bord2\blur4}Next Episode\N{\fs30\fscy150}Shibuya Incident - Gate, Open
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.56,0:23:50.88,Main,Ieiri,0000,0000,0000,,He's rich, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.88,0:23:53.12,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're such a kidder, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.12,0:23:54.80,Main,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, don't discount what she said.

